carried me away.

41:14.043 --> 41:15.644
That was a good move.

41:16.913 --> 41:18.047
The only good thing
that ever came

41:18.047 --> 41:20.349
out of the
telephone company.

41:21.984 --> 41:24.520
In the span of five years,

41:24.520 --> 41:30.026
I lost both Bobbie...
now Dorothy.

41:30.026 --> 41:32.394
Death...
It's the one injustice

41:32.394 --> 41:33.595
that is universal.

41:33.595 --> 41:38.034
It's the great injustice
that you have to deal with.

41:38.034 --> 41:40.937
**

